    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >90 年代的波兰梦在等着你！失业率急剧上升，市场空前自由。这是成为企业家的最佳时机。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126490/extras/d7c3baf2b48336a336122a4634e5fb56.poster.avif?t=1756035531\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126490/extras/d7c3baf2b48336a336122a4634e5fb56.webm?t=1756035531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126490/extras/d7c3baf2b48336a336122a4634e5fb56.mp4?t=1756035531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管理您的当铺</strong><br><br>作为一名新晋的企业主，你必须亲力亲为。购买各种物品，从厨房用具到艺术品。整理商品，充分利用空间。与顾客讨价还价，尽可能得到最好的交易。积累利润，发展业务。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126490/extras/70777519c1eab72d901fbd1c499ff301.poster.avif?t=1756035531\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126490/extras/70777519c1eab72d901fbd1c499ff301.webm?t=1756035531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126490/extras/70777519c1eab72d901fbd1c499ff301.mp4?t=1756035531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发挥创意</strong><br><br>缺钱？做点副业，赚点外快。卖盗版 CD。垃圾箱潜水。销赃。收集废品。拆卸物品。把握机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126490/extras/f78924dec7debaecc1555cf595284309.poster.avif?t=1756035531\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126490/extras/f78924dec7debaecc1555cf595284309.webm?t=1756035531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126490/extras/f78924dec7debaecc1555cf595284309.mp4?t=1756035531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装饰和升级</strong><br><br>定制墙壁和地板，吸引更多顾客。扩建当铺，摆放更多商品。购买更好的家具以提高销售额。设计您的商店，提高效率。</p>",
